---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="ToolMixr terms of service.">

  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using ToolMixr (toolmixr.com), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>ToolMixr provides free online tools for developers, designers, and content creators. All tools are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>3. Use of Tools</h2>
      <p>You may use ToolMixr's tools for personal and commercial purposes. You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the tools for any illegal purpose</li>
        <li>Attempt to disrupt or overload the service</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer or modify the service</li>
        <li>Use automated scripts to access the service excessively</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>The content, design, and code of ToolMixr are owned by ToolMixr. You may not copy, modify, or distribute the site's source code without permission. Output generated by the tools belongs to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>ToolMixr is provided "as is" and "as available." We make no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the accuracy, reliability, or availability of the tools. Use the output at your own risk.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>In no event shall ToolMixr be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use the service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>ToolMixr may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the content or practices of these third parties.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@toolmixr.com">legal@toolmixr.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 40px 0 80px; max-width: 720px; }
  .legal-page h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal-page .updated { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 14px; }
  .legal-section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .legal-section h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal-section p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal-section ul { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 24px; }
  .legal-section ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
</style>
